description:
The Apostles' Creed | Faith Matters | Episode 7 | All That Debt | Dr. N.T. Wright

Watch The Apostles' Creed: Faith Matters Episode 7 All That Debt on Vision Video 

Join an esteemed panel of scholars as they explore the Apostles' Creed. In this final episode, they explore forgiveness of sin, and the great Christian hope of resurrection and eternal life with God.

"I believe in the Holy Spirit, the holy catholic church, the communion of saints, the forgiveness of sins, the resurrection of the body, and life everlasting…" Join an esteemed panel of scholars as they explore the Apostles' Creed. In this final episode, they explore forgiveness of sin, and the great Christian hope of resurrection and eternal life with God.

Director: T.N. Mohan
Starring: Dr. N.T. Wright, Dr. Robert Mulholland, Dr. Alister McGrath, Dr. Derek Tidball, Dr. Kallistos Ware, Dr. Martin Marty, Dr. William Johnson, Dr. Peter Contrell, Rev. Richard Bewes, Dr. Timothy Dudley-Smith,
